name: Deutsche Bibliothek Database
description: Deutsche Bibliothek Database is a union catalog of the records of National Library of Germany, the Deutsche Bibliothek. The database includes the holdings of the Deutsche Bucherei Leipzig, the Deutsche Bibliothek Frankfurt am Main, and the Deutsches Musikarchiv Berlin. The database includes the Anne-Frank-Shoah-Bibliothek, watermarks, paper samples, the Reichsbibliothek of 1848 Socialistica, posters, patents, and documents of international organizations.
